between these formal categories, as its content also bridges the gap
between the law, morals and politics; it can also serve to cover up
the boundary between factuality and normativity. Among other things,
the author deals with responsibility in police law, product liability,
personal responsibility in municipal self-government, in
responsibility for the environment, ensuring liability, responsibility
for public welfare, the discourse on the sharing of responsibility in
