profession, students and practitioners in the complex art of pleading
as well as in the infinite particulars, the technical intricacies and
linguistic antiquities, of the English law of property. This, in other
words, as its title states, is an institutional work, a treatise on
law, an exercise in written reason and if not scripture at least heavy
writing. Start then with the first incident of an extended image
