AB  - Technological changes and the development of an economy based on
concepts and practices such as "innovation", "collaboration" and
"information" has been causing a cultural change in society and a
reorganization in the provision of legal services. After observing
several legal sites, we noticed that they present different meanings
in relation to the imagery construction of the Law in Communication.
And from there, we decided to research how the legal area is being
resignified on the web and what meanings these sites are attributing
to the legal field in the construction of their interfaces, their
images and imaginaries.
