Ruth Blufarb, Monika Fludernik, Jeanne Gaakeer, Dominique Hipp,
Claudia Lieb, Hans J. Lind, Arild Linneberg, Frode Helmich Pedersen,
Frank Schäfer, Peter Schneck, Robert Spoo, Klaus Stierstorfer, Ulrike
Tabbert and Claire Wrobel.
