social conflicts. We will approach the transition from Symbolic
Legislation to Symbolic Constitutionalisation, establishing, based on
Luhmann, the differentiation of autopoiesis and allopathies of the
law. Finally, we will cover the implications of Symbolic
Constitutionalisation for the Legal System, the main being: Systemic
Corruption.
